reviewText: Save your money. All of these interviews are available on-line. Buy tickets to her concert or her live albums/dvd's. What. A. Waste.
Kind of bought it without reading the description in full.  Bit to rough and unofficial for my taste.  And yet it is still about the amazing Sara Bareilles so have to give it at least 3 stars.
Repetitive stories, poor information and details...
As a big fan of Sara I loved every minute of this DVD!
Sara Bareilles is awesome as always

Wish I had waited for a review on this before purchasing. Don't waste your money. Nothing new here. All video interviews that make up this DVD are available on YouTube. And the commentary is general information from a source like Wikepedia.

I hate to repeat myself, the comments I made on another post said it all, but I wanted it registered as a verified purchase etc. Yes, I did buy it. Yes I really like her music, and have been to concerts-she is a great live performer. This  however I would like to send back, but just won't. It states "unauthorized" on the DVD cover with no liner or booklet, so someone just mostly did a rip-off it seems to me. She is coming to my area soon "San Francisco Bay Area" , so I will go to that concert to make up for it. Save your money. Really.

Just a a few interviews thrown together with narration. You could probably find every one of these interviews on you tube if you searched for 3 minutes. I love her voice and I wanted to learn more intimate details about the artist,but this dvd offers absolutely
nothing other than stock footage. I'm not one to write reviews but after purchasing a product so inferior it borders on theft then I must speak.
